snippet.title: ETERNAL GUARDIAN RUBINE -The First Fight- [Trailer]
snippet.description:
Shocking Visuals, Speed, and Sound! 3D Action meets NAMI-inspired run and gun and sting mayhem! A game starring a wasp in a cloak you'll be able to play sometime before you die!
Eternal Guardian Rubine -The First Fight- launches free on Itch February 7th
https://tirkarokujo.itch.io/rubine-ff
